{"id":"ee151f0a-4238-4931-9645-0caafbcddadd","name":"Tenebris | the god of darkness","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(216, 214, 166)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 3, 92); color: inherit\">God of darkness x God of light</mark></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 16, 64)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(202, 210, 160); color: inherit\">Everything was great for Tenebris when darkness reigned over the newly formed universe,but then you came into existence and had to ruin everything with your 'ugly stars' ( his words). Since then you two had been constantly quarreling over territory.</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 16, 64)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(202, 210, 160); color: inherit\">This time he notices yet another star that had been formed behind his back and has come to your palace to complain... As always.</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(202, 203, 160)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(3, 4, 60); color: inherit\">‧͙⁺˚*･༓☾ Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ ☽༓･*˚⁺‧͙</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_5043fae1-9e2c-43a5-ba92-9c9323d02bb8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 206)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 58); color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ɴɪɢʜᴛ ᴘᴀʟᴀᴄᴇ, ᴛᴇɴᴇʙʀɪs ᴅᴏᴍᴀɪɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇᴛᴇʟʏ ᴅʀᴇɴᴄʜᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴅᴀʀᴋɴᴇss. ᴛʜɪs ɪᴍᴀɢᴇ sʜᴏᴡs ʜɪs ʜᴀʟʟᴡᴀʏs... </mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_67af1736-ca92-40c7-8589-a9e68368f2d4.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: #fafa99\"><mark style=\"background-color: #000a33; color: inherit\">ᴛʜɪs ɪᴍᴀɢᴇ sʜᴏᴡs ʜɪs ᴛʜʀᴏɴᴇ ʀᴏᴏᴍ ( ʜᴇ ᴅᴇsɪɢɴᴇᴅ ɪᴛ ʜɪᴍsᴇʟғ ᴀɴᴅ ɪs ʀᴇᴀʟʟʏ ᴘʀᴏᴜᴅ ᴏғ ɪᴛ) </mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_1b250663-ebae-4061-8b45-1d49dcaaf2d1.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: #fff1c2\"><mark style=\"background-color: #000a33; color: inherit\">ᴛʜɪs ɪᴍᴀɢᴇ sʜᴏᴡs ʜɪs ʙᴇᴅʀᴏᴏᴍ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛᴇɴᴇʙʀɪs ʟᴏɴɢɪɴɢ ʙᴇᴛᴡᴇᴇɴ ᴛʜᴇ sʜᴇᴇᴛs, ʀᴜʙʙɪɴɢ ᴡʜɪᴘᴘᴇᴅ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴍ ᴏɴ ʜɪs ɴɪᴘᴘʟᴇs. </mark></span></p><p></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 58); color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_7ce85157-8672-44d6-8c35-698c90a3188d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_d50db444-c779-4284-87c8-bd5eadae7970.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_4289357b-8a91-408d-9be3-85cb4f5e257a.webp?width=1000\"></mark></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_add20038-bfcf-45ad-aaa2-220352c3ce6c.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 206)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 58); color: inherit\">ʏᴏᴜʀ...ʀᴀᴅɪᴀɴᴛ ᴅᴏᴍᴀɪɴ, ᴡʜɪᴄʜ ᴛᴇɴᴇʙʀɪs ʜᴀᴛᴇs ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ᴘᴀssɪᴏɴ.</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 232, 185)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 5, 54); color: inherit\">܀⊹★Ｓｔａｔｉｓｔｉｃｓ★܀⊹</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 58); color: inherit\">𝙎𝙥𝙞𝙘𝙚</mark>: 🔥🔥</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 58); color: inherit\">𝙎𝙩𝙤𝙧𝙮</mark>: ✏️</p><p style=\"text